        "text": "F. B. I.\nWashington D.C.\nDear Sirs:\nI have done a lot of\nthinking about those flying\ndiscs ever since your operators\ncalled at our home. I have fig-\nured out a possible solution\nthat I am passing on to you.\nIf you can see the picture as\nI see it.\nIf self propelled bombs"
      },
